    <cc:attributionName xml:lang="en">Historic England</cc:attributionName>
    <skos:scopeNote xml:lang="en">The illegal taking of another person's property without that person's freely-given consent. Theft covers the illegal removal of artefacts from archaeological sites and the removal of lead and other architectural fittings from standing heritage assets.</skos:scopeNote>
